《不可思议城镇》通常受到了媒体的好评。评价汇总网站[[Game_Rankings|Game Rankings]]上，游戏的平均分是86%（48个评价）<ref name="gr" />。而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，游戏的平均分为85/100（57个评价）<ref name="mc" />。对于将“脑筋急转弯”与冒险风格结合的游戏设定，媒体的评价褒贬不一。一些评论认为游戏成功的将二者结合起来<ref name="Gamespot review" />，[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]的评价称游戏的制作手法远胜于融入游戏环境的难题<ref name="1UP review" />。而另一些评论则表示游戏并没有将二者很好地融合，[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]的评论表示，在玩家忙于解决无数小谜题的之时，主线剧情之谜已经基本暴露于玩家面前了<ref name="Game Informer review" />。有评论称游戏重玩一遍的价值不大，一旦所有的难题得到解决后，就再没有什么要素值得重玩了<ref name="IGN review" />。游戏的呈现，如常规欧洲动画风格的过场动画受到了评论的赞赏<ref name="Gamespot review" /><ref name="IGN review" />。《Hyper》杂志的达伦·威尔斯因“巧妙地理念，大量的求解与解锁及意想不到的呈现”而称赞了游戏。然而他也批评了“解一些谜题时放着音乐令人可恼”<ref>{{cite journal|last=Wells|first=Darren|date=June 2008|title=Professor Layton and the Curious Village|journal=[[Hyper_(magazine)|Hyper]]|publisher=[[Next_Media|Next Media]]|issue=176|pages=60|issn=1320-7458}}</ref>。《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》将游戏结尾列入任天堂主机游戏最佳结尾中，其理由是玩家的许多发现都是在尾声之中<ref>{{cite book |title=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] 250th issue! |year=2010 |publisher=[[Future_US|Future US]] |location=[[South_San_Francisco,_California|South San Francisco, California]] |pages=46 |accessdate=2010-07-24}}</ref>。

《不可思议城镇》2007年在日本售出70万份<ref>{{cite web | url = http://ds.ign.com/articles/840/840183p1.html | title = Professor Layton Tops the Charts | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | first = Anoop | last = Gantayat | date = 2007-12-07 | accessdate = 2008-05-30 | archive-date = 2013-01-28 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6E0yjDLVE?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/12/07/professor-layton-tops-the-charts | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在北美，游戏发售前三周都占据着任天堂DS游戏销量榜之首.<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17417 | title = Saling The World: Professor Layton Tops North American DS Charts | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2008-02-15 | accessdate = 2008-05-30 | first = Danny | last = Cowan | archive-date = 2013-01-28 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6E0yk2AmJ?url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17417 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17553 | title = Saling The World: Professor Layton, Apollo Justice Impact DS Charts in U.S. | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2008-02-22 | accessdate = 2008-05-30 | first = Danny | last = Cowan | archive-date = 2012-10-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121013172355/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=17553 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/column_index.php?story=8821 | title = Saling The World: The Sims 2: FreeTime, Gundam Lead Worldwide Charts | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2008-02-29 | accessdate = 2008-05-30 | first = Danny | last = Cowan | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091108234229/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/column_index.php?story=8821 | archivedate = 2009-11-08 }}</ref>。游戏在英国重新进货后，《雷顿教授》的销量增长了65%，并从销量榜第10名排到了第四名<ref>{{cite web |title=UK - Professor Layton Makes Big Jump, Skate 2 Sales Down |url=http://chartget.com/2009/02/uk-professor-layton-makes-big-jump.html |publisher=Chart Get |accessdate=2009-02-07 |date=2008-10-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090605101944/http://chartget.com/2009/02/uk-professor-layton-makes-big-jump.html |archivedate=2009-06-05 }}</ref>。

=== 奖项 ===

《雷顿教授与不可思议城镇》获得了2008年度[[电子游戏颁奖盛典|电子游戏颁奖盛典]]之最佳掌机游戏奖{{Citation needed|date=December 2008}}，[[GameSpy|GameSpy]] 2008年度最佳任天堂游戏奖<ref name="gamespyds">{{cite web |title=GameSpy - DS Top 5 |url=http://goty.gamespy.com/2008/ds/6.html |accessdate=2008-12-21 |date=2008-12-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081220053732/http://goty.gamespy.com/2008/ds/6.html |archivedate=2008-12-20 }}</ref>及GameSpy 2008年度全平台十佳游戏奖<ref name="gamespy2008">{{cite web |title=GameSpy - Overall Top 10 |url=http://goty.gamespy.com/2008/overall/index.html |accessdate=2008-12-21 |date=2008-12-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081223103558/http://goty.gamespy.com/2008/overall/index.html |archivedate=2008-12-23 }}</ref>。2009年3月，游戏获得了[[英国学会电子游戏奖|英国学会电子游戏奖]]之最佳掌机奖。在IGN 2008年度电子游戏奖中，游戏获任天堂DS最佳益智游戏奖的提名<ref name="ignpuzzle">{{cite web |title=IGN DS: Best Puzzle Game 2008 |url=http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/5.html |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]].com |accessdate=2008-12-19 |date=2008-12-15 |archive-date=2008-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219041622/http://bestof.ign.com/2008/ds/5.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同时游戏还获2008儿童BATFA最佳电子游戏奖的提名<ref>[http://www.bafta.org/awards/childrens/nominations-childrens-awards-in-2008,593,BA.html BAFTA Children's Awards 2008 nominees] {{webarchive|url=https://www.webcitation.org/69fw6pVPE?url=http://www.bafta.org/awards/childrens/nominations-childrens-awards-in-2008,593,BA.html |date=2012-08-04 }}, bafta.org</ref>。游戏成为了GiantBomb 2008年度最佳任天堂DS游戏<ref>[http://www.giantbomb.com/features/best-of-2008/1/?category=11 Game of the Year 2008: Best DS Game] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090603083707/http://www.giantbomb.com/features/best-of-2008/1/?category=11 |date=2009-06-03 }}, giantbomb.com</ref>。《雷顿教授与不可思议城镇》选入了被Eurogamer 2008年之15个年度游戏<ref>[http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/eurogamers-top-50-games-of-2008-20-11-article?page=3 Eurogamer's Top 50 Games of 2008], eurogamer.net</ref>及GameSpy的2008年年度DS游戏<ref>[http://goty.gamespy.com/2008/ds/6.html DS Top 5] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081220053732/http://goty.gamespy.com/2008/ds/6.html |date=2008-12-20 }}, 2008, gamespy.com</ref>。游戏还获得了《任天堂力量》杂志“年度最佳益智游戏”奖。在2009年2月，《雷顿教授与不可思议城镇》获得由Adventure Gamers颁发Aggie奖之最佳家用机/掌机冒险游戏奖一等奖<ref name="aggie">{{cite web |title=The Aggies: 2008 Award Presentation |url=http://www.adventuregamers.com/article/id,981/p,16 |publisher=[[AdventureGamers|AdventureGamers]].com |accessdate=2009-02-18 |date=2009-02-18}}</ref>。游戏在2008年G4 G-phoria上被提名最佳掌机游戏奖。

== 音乐 ==
收录了游戏中出现所有音乐的原声碟名为《雷顿教授与不可思议城镇原声音乐》（{{lang|ja|レイトン教授と不思議な町 オリジナル・サウンドトラック}}），并仅在日本发售。音乐略受法国风的影响。原声碟由[[西浦智仁|西浦智仁]]作曲<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.squareenixmusic.com/reviews/mactear/professorlayton.shtml |title= Professor Layton and the Curious Village Original Soundtrack :: Review by Mac_Tear|publisher= squareenixmusic.com}}</ref>。

